Package tmp

Class Port

  • java.lang.Object
    • tmp.Port
  • public class Port
extends java.lang.Object
    Since:
    01/29/2019 Ports hold Commodities that are bought and sold to Merchants. Merchants travel from one to another using Routes. Ports have a functionally unlimited amount of gold.
    Author:
    Michael Bianconi
